# Writing Studio — Agent Instructions

At the **very beginning** of every new conversation about this project:

1. Read `ROADMAP.md` in the project root
2. Briefly remind the user what's on the roadmap (keep it to a few bullet points)
3. Ask if they want to work on any of those items in this session

This ensures continuity across sessions and avoids re-explaining context.
